headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  PAPERT, FREDERIC S

snippet: PAPERT--Frederic S. The Board of Directors of Carnegie Hill Neighbors mourns the passing of Frederic S. Papert, one of the founders (in 1970) and the first president of CHN. His mission to preserve the architectural heritage of Carnegie Hill continues to this day. 1/3
